title: Ep - 106 - REAL HOUSEWIVES OF ORANGE COUNTY VINTAGE EPISODE REVIEW
description:
In this crossover bonus episode Ronnie Karam from Watch What Crappens and Rose Pricks podcasts helps Kate dissect a vintage episode of Real Housewives of Orange County, one of Kate's favorite episodes. 


Season 7, Episode 14


Slade takes Heather engagement ring shopping for Gretchen, Alexis throws a puppies and princesses thee d birthday party for her twins, Tamra gets a tattoo removed, and Vicki and Briana fight about her new boyfriend Brooks.
